ner":"container","background_color":"","content_liquid":"<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-678b21b3-7fff-8c7a-b1de-e9256c208d3d\">\n        <h3 dir=\"ltr\">What are the Trends in Lighting for 2025?<\/h3>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">1. Energy efficiency<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Eco-friendly lighting options are in high demand. LED modules are popular for their energy efficiency and long lifespan.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Ledsone’s Contribution:<\/strong> Explore our range of LED products that blend style with eco-friendliness.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">2. Minimalist Designs<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Sleek and simple lighting fixtures are dominating trends.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Examples:<\/strong> Modern ceiling lights for living rooms with matte finishes in black, brass, or white.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">3. Smart Lighting<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Smart lighting systems offer convenience and personalization through apps or voice control.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Suggestions:<\/strong> Choose smart living room light fittings for enhanced functionality and control.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">4. Layered Ceiling Lighting<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Combining recessed lights, pendant lights, and chandeliers adds depth and dimension to your living room.<\/p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3 dir=\"ltr\">How Can I Light My Living Room Without Overhead Lights?<\/h3>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">If your living room lacks overhead lighting, you can still achieve excellent lighting:<\/p>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">1. Floor Lamps<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Tall and elegant floor lamps provide ample ambient lighting.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Example:<\/strong> Place an arc floor lamp in the corner to light up the seating area.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">2. Wall Lights<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Mounted wall lights create a cozy atmosphere while saving space.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Options:<\/strong> Adjustable wall sconces or decorative fixtures.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">3. Table Lamps<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Table lamps are both functional and decorative.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Use lamps with patterned shades to add visual interest.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">4. LED Strips<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">LED strips offer a modern touch when placed under shelves, furniture, or along walls.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Suggestion:<\/strong> Pair LED strips with dimmers for adjustable mood lighting.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3 dir=\"ltr\">Lighting Ideas for Living Rooms<\/h3>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">1. Ceiling Lamps for Living Rooms<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Choose ceiling lamps that complement your living room’s decor.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Examples:<\/strong> Statement chandeliers, flush-mounted fixtures, or modern ceiling light fittings.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">2. Living Room Ceiling Lighting Ideas<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Experiment with a mix of recessed lights and pendant lights for a dynamic look.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Use ceiling lighting to create focal points in your living room.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">3. Living Room Modern Ceiling Lights<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Modern designs bring sophistication and functionality to your space.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Options:<\/strong> Opt for sleek, geometric ceiling light fixtures in metallic finishes.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">4. Lighting for Small Living Rooms<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Maximize light in compact spaces with clever solutions.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Suggestions:<\/strong> Use mirrors to reflect light and choose compact yet powerful ceiling light fixtures.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n    <\/span>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"gallery_aFQW4d":{"type":"gallery","blocks":{"image_renDfq":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/PLTYBC_WCBNBC_ICST64E2740.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-table-lamp"}},"image_dmxDrd":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Modern_Ceramic_Base_Table_Lamp_28df827e-e6e2-4419-9c9e-02f71cd0e9f2.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-table-lamp"}},"image_9bg8Bz":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/09_5_2a33c0c7-ce8a-4f45-929c-8f44f249fb4d.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/desk-lamp-wood-bedside-table-lamp-plugin-light"}},"image_A4MV6U":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/o_dUWfHrN2eb.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/colorful-mosaic-lamp-for-uk"}}},"block_order":["image_renDfq","image_dmxDrd","image_9bg8Bz","image_A4MV6U"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Transform Your Space with Beautiful Table Lamps","description":"","text_align":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","layout_type":"carousel","column_gap":30,"aspect_ratio":"original","custom_ratio":"21:9","actions_click":"unset","custom_column":3,"grid_image_desktop":4,"autoplay":false,"loop":false,"show_arrow":false,"show_bullet":true,"show_bullet_mobile":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_liquid_CAHxTN":{"type":"custom-liquid","settings":{"heading":"","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","content_liquid":"<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-678b21b3-7fff-8c7a-b1de-e9256c208d3d\">\n        <h3 dir=\"ltr\">Final Tips for Choosing Lights for Your Living Room<\/h3>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">1. Consider Your Room’s Size<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Pick lighting proportional to your living room’s dimensions.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Example:<\/strong> A large chandelier might overwhelm a small room, but flush-mounted ceiling lights work perfectly.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">2. Match Your Décor Style<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Your lighting should complement the overall design of your living room.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Modern ceiling lights for living rooms are ideal for contemporary spaces.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <h4 dir=\"ltr\">3. Prioritize Energy Efficiency<\/h4>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">LED lights save energy and last longer, making them a smart choice.<\/p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Ledsone’s Range:<\/strong> Explore our collection of energy-efficient LED modules and light fittings.<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3 dir=\"ltr\">Conclusion<\/h3>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Proper lighting can elevate your living room’s ambiance and functionality. By layering ambient, task, and accent lighting, you can create a space that’s both inviting and stylish. Embrace trends like minimalist designs, smart lighting, and eco-friendliness to keep your living room modern and energy-efficient.<\/p>\n        <p dir=\"ltr\">Ledsone offers pendant lights, wall lights, and LED modules to create your ideal living room lighting. Explore our living room lighting collection to find the perfect fit for your home!<\/p>\n    <\/span>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}}},"order":["divider_8BUdXc","main-collection-heading","8498460c-0376-40d1-bafc-199edbe0edfc","439e38df-206c-40a8-9cd5-fc0e5f00f9d3","product-grid","b1a1633c-9de0-43c8-8a60-a0eddc69dfb1","47b4aaae-a5a7-401b-a79c-d7b0652caf69","divider_PhNww8","custom_text_qedYj9","banner_image_bUhTqD","custom_liquid_BPkHwA","gallery_rdw6wK","custom_liquid_NKDQi4","gallery_aFQW4d","custom_liquid_CAHxTN"]}